data.description: Be one of the first residents to live in Del Webb North Penn!!! A brand new Luxury Active Adult community with NEW CONSTRUCTION homes, resort style amenities with a full time Lifestyle Director. This beautiful home with everything picked out by a design professional offers an open layout with beautiful finishes and loads of upgrades included. Move in June 2022 and take advantage of early community pricing! Photos are of model homes in other communities but representative of the spaces inside this home.
